'''HenJ GrafX Calendar 2006''' was produced by [[Henning Janssen]] and features illustrations by Henning Janssen. The calendar was produced in a limited edition run of 111.

* Dimensions: 11 3/4 x 11 3/4 inches
* Wire bound
* Heavy wire hanging loop
